### 二手交易平台认证接口测试文件
### 测试环境配置：使用 http-client.env.json 中的 baseUrl

## 1. 用户注册接口测试

### 1.1 正常注册测试 - 成功创建新用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser2024",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户2024",
  "phone": "13987654321"
}

### 1.2 注册失败 - 用户名已存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "nickname": "重复用户测试",
  "phone": "13812345678"
}

### 1.3 注册失败 - 密码确认不匹配
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser_wrongpwd",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "654321",
  "nickname": "密码不匹配测试",
  "phone": "13712345678"
}

### 1.4 注册失败 - 用户名格式不符合要求（包含特殊字符）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test-user-invalid",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "nickname": "用户名格式错误",
  "phone": "13612345678"
}

### 1.5 注册失败 - 用户名长度不足
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ab",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "nickname": "用户名太短",
  "phone": "13512345678"
}

### 1.6 注册失败 - 手机号格式不正确
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser_invalidphone",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "nickname": "手机号格式错误",
  "phone": "12345678901"
}

### 1.7 注册失败 - 必填字段为空
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "nickname": "缺少用户名",
  "phone": "13412345678"
}

## 2. 用户登录接口测试

### 2.1 正常登录测试 - 使用默认管理员账户
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2.2 登录失败 - 用户不存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nonexistent_user",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2.3 登录失败 - 密码错误
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrong_password"
}

### 2.4 登录失败 - 参数缺失（缺少密码）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin"
}

### 2.5 登录失败 - 参数为空
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "password": ""
}

### 3. 用户状态检查接口测试（未登录状态）

### 3.1 检查登录状态（未登录）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/check-login

### 3.2 获取用户信息（未登录）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/info

## 4. 登录后功能测试

### 4.1 用户登录获取token
# @name user_login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4.2 提取登录token用于后续请求
@user_token = {{user_login.response.body.$.data.token}}

### 4.3 检查登录状态（已登录）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/check-login
Authorization: {{user_token}}

### 4.4 获取用户信息（已登录）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/info
Authorization: {{user_token}}

## 5. 用户登出测试

### 5.1 用户登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: {{user_token}}

### 5.2 登出后检查登录状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/check-login

### 5.3 登出后尝试获取用户信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/info
Authorization: {{user_token}}

## 6. 管理员登录接口测试

### 6.1 管理员正常登录
# @name admin_login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 6.2 提取管理员token
@admin_token = {{admin_login.response.body.$.data.token}}

### 6.3 管理员检查登录状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/admin/check-login
Authorization: {{admin_token}}

### 6.4 获取管理员信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/admin/info
Authorization: {{admin_token}}

## 7. 管理员登出测试

### 7.1 管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/admin/logout
Authorization: {{admin_token}}

### 7.2 管理员登出后检查状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/admin/check-login

## 8. 并发登录测试

### 8.1 同一用户多次登录（测试Sa-Token并发配置）
# @name first_login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

@first_token = {{first_login.response.body.$.data.token}}

### 8.2 同一用户第二次登录
# @name second_login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

@second_token = {{second_login.response.body.$.data.token}}

### 8.3 验证两个token都能正常使用
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/check-login
Authorization: {{first_token}}

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/check-login
Authorization: {{second_token}}

## 9. Token有效性测试

### 9.1 使用无效token访问受保护资源
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/info
Authorization: invalid_token_123456

### 9.2 使用空token访问受保护资源
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/info
Authorization: 

### 9.3 不带Authorization头访问受保护资源
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/info

## 10. 注册后立即登录测试

### 10.1 注册新用户
# @name register_new_user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser_{{randomInt(1000,9999)}}",
  "password": "password123",
  "confirmPassword": "password123",
  "nickname": "新注册用户",
  "phone": "139{{randomInt(10000000,99999999)}}"
}

@register_username = {{register_new_user.response.body.$.data.username}}

### 10.2 使用刚注册的用户登录
# @name login_new_user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{register_username}}",
  "password": "password123"
}

@new_user_token = {{login_new_user.response.body.$.data.token}}

### 10.3 验证新用户登录状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/check-login
Authorization: {{new_user_token}}

### 10.4 获取新用户信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/info
Authorization: {{new_user_token}}